data.description: This beautiful home has been tastefully updated. The home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, brand new laminate flooring throughout, new paint inside and out, and 2 car carport. The kitchen was designed with exotic granite countertops, new cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. The bathrooms are done with the same exotic granite and cabinets as the kitchen with tiled showers. Don't miss the opportunity to make this dream home your reality. Call today to schedule your private showing.
